#

Lemon Garlic Shrimp Bisque

$15.99
350 kcal
Difficulty: 60%

Allergens:

shellfishdairy

Dietary Tags:

gluten-freelow-carbpaleo

Tags:

soupseafoodcomfort foodgourmet

Description

A creamy and zesty shrimp bisque, infused with saffron and a hint of cayenne for a warm finish, paired perfectly with garlic bread.

Ingredients

  • shrimp: 1 lb
  • fish stock: 4 cups
  • heavy cream: 1 cup
  • butter: 2 tbsp
  • garlic: 4 cloves
  • lemon juice: 1/4 cup
  • saffron threads: 1/4 tsp
  • cayenne pepper: 1/2 tsp
  • onion: 1 medium
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • crusty bread: 4 slices
